#V  POS_DATA_TYPE . . . . . . . . position where the data of a type is stored
#V  POS_NUMB_TYPE . . . . . . . position where the number of a type is stored
#V  POS_FIRST_FREE_TYPE . . . . .  first position that has no overall meaning
